PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784701089
OL,3,CRussian warship conducted weapon
OL,4,Cfiring exercise off the coast of
OL,5,CPlymouth
OL,7,FIn a statement on Tuesday the Ministry
OL,8,Fof Defence confirmed the Russian ship
OL,9,Fhad conducted a "live-fire weapons
OL,10,Fexercise in international waters."
OL,12,FIt added: "The Royal Navy monitored
OL,13,Fthat exercise throughout, continues to
OL,14,Ftrack the vessel's activity closely,
OL,15,Fand stands ready to protect UK
OL,16,Fnational security."
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
