PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784701089
OL,3,CRussian warship conducted weapon
OL,4,Cfiring exercise off the coast of
OL,5,CPlymouth
OL,7,FThe incident comes less than six weeks
OL,8,Fafter a Russian shadow fleet carrying
OL,9,Foil was intercepted by British troops,
OL,10,Fin the first UK-led operation to
OL,11,Fcapture a sanctioned vessel.
OL,13,FThe Royal Navy said it carried out a
OL,14,Fthree-month long "unbroken watch" on
OL,15,FRussian warships and accompanying
OL,16,Fvessels in and around UK water.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
