OL,3,CRussian warship conducted weapon
OL,4,Cfiring exercise off the coast of
OL,5,CPlymouth
OL,7,FIn June a British couple told ITV News
OL,8,Fabout their encounter with a Russian
OL,9,Fwarship that fired warning shots while
OL,10,Fthey were sailing their Yacht in the
OL,11,FChannel.
OL,13,FDefence was a heated topic under Sir
OL,14,FKeir Starmer's premiership as his
OL,15,Fdefence investment plan (Dip) left a
OL,16,F#4.7 billion black hole in funding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
